635
00:38:44,410 --> 00:38:45,310
So

636
00:38:49,430 --> 00:38:50,920
I hope to guard it with you.

637
00:39:05,320 --> 00:39:07,180
Welcome.

638
00:39:09,290 --> 00:39:10,180
What’s up?

639
00:39:10,620 --> 00:39:12,060
Come in, please.

640
00:39:14,010 --> 00:39:15,450
What are you doing?

641
00:39:25,790 --> 00:39:28,090
