come for a check today?

642
00:39:28,690 --> 00:39:30,280
I didn’t receive any notice.

643
00:39:30,610 --> 00:39:31,580
Boss.

644
00:39:31,780 --> 00:39:33,620
Tonghao asked us to do it.

645
00:39:33,640 --> 00:39:35,620
Do you think our hotel is revitalized again?

646
00:39:35,840 --> 00:39:38,260
Boss, I haven’t seen

647
00:39:38,280 --> 00:39:40,490
