656
00:40:01,360 --> 00:40:02,460
OK.

657
00:40:02,920 --> 00:40:03,480
What?

658
00:40:04,050 --> 00:40:05,470
Who gave you the financial statements?

659
00:40:09,070 --> 00:40:10,160
Fengqiao,

660
00:40:12,540 --> 00:40:13,710
you always lose your stance

661
00:40:13,730 --> 00:40:15,280
whenever you see a handsome guy.

662
00:40:15,820 --> 00:40:16,730
How dare you disclose

663
00:40:16,750 --> 00:40:18,400
such trade secrets to others?

664
00:40:20,790 --> 00:40:21,980
Everybody knows that

665
00:40:22,000 --> 00:40:23,350
Guanmei Hotel loses more than

666
00:40:23,370 --> 00:40:24,760
one hundred thousand yuan every month.

