669
00:40:27,480 --> 00:40:28,230
Me.

670
00:40:30,320 --> 00:40:31,610
But I am not a fly.

671
00:40:36,550 --> 00:40:37,240
Mr. Tang,

672
00:40:37,730 --> 00:40:39,670
if you want to refit Guanmei Hotel,

673
00:40:40,480 --> 00:40:43,070
I think you should change
your management philosophy.

674
00:40:43,510 --> 00:40:45,570
Guanmei Hotel’s loss keeps increasing now.

675
00:40:45,590 --> 00:40:46,710
The fundamental reason

676
00:40:46,730 --> 00:40:47,160
actually lies in

677
00:40:47,180 --> 00:40:49,450
your failure to improve total quality management.

678
00:40:50,130 --> 00:40:50,870
What?

679
00:40:51,140 --> 00:40:52,320
Total what?

680
00:40:52,870 --> 00:40:54,810
TQM. Total quality management.

681
00:40:58,140 --> 00:40:59,840
Without total quality management,

682
00:41:00,140 --> 00:41:03,170
guest satisfaction tracking system and

683
00:41:03,190 --> 00:41:05,390
integrated business plan,

684
00:41:05,410 --> 00:41:06,590
you will know nothing about

685
00:41:06,610 --> 00:41:10,250
Guanmei Hotel’s market penetration index.

686
00:41:10,800 --> 00:41:11,730
Guanmei Hotel

687
00:41:11,750 --> 00:41:13,970
needs comprehensive and systematized management.

688
00:41:13,990 --> 00:41:15,720
Mr. Tang, you can just check

689
00:41:15,740 --> 00:41:18,070
the negative comment ratio
of Guanmei Hotel on MT website.

690
00:41:19,280 --> 00:41:20,740
Customer experience is fundamental

691
00:41:20,760 --> 00:41:21,860
of a hotel’s survival.

692
00:41:21,880 --> 00:41:23,430
A hotel without good customer experiences

693
00:41:23,450 --> 00:41:25,320
will only have poor customer comments.

694
00:41:25,340 --> 00:41:27,120
If you want to change the hotel,

695
00:41:27,470 --> 00:41:29,240
you need to firstly

696
00:41:29,680 --> 00:41:30,840
change your philosophies.

697
00:41:30,860 --> 00:41:32,930
Operated in the name of a hotel,

698
00:41:33,170 --> 00:41:33,760
Guanmei Hotel actually doesn’t

699
00:41:33,780 --> 00:41:35,390
have the base and capability to run a hotel.

700
00:41:35,570 --> 00:41:36,350
I recommend

701
00:41:36,580 --> 00:41:38,880
renaming Guanmei Hotel as Guanmei Inn

702
00:41:39,080 --> 00:41:40,600
